name: Sponsored Families
query:
select center,region,father,tabFather.nationality,tabFather.social_number,tabSponsorship.start_date,tabSponsorship.end_date
from tabFamily
join tabSponsorship on tabSponsorship.family = tabFamily.name 
where tabSponsorship.start_date <= %(date_on)s
and %(date_on)s <= tabSponsorship.end_date
